None of `AudioPlayer.tsx`, `Reader.tsx`, `BookMap.tsx`, `Library.tsx`, `NavBar.tsx`, `Cover.tsx` have component tests. Highest-value scenarios:

- **`AudioPlayer`**: renders `null` while `tts.status === 'idle'` (easy, high-value regression guard); `cycleRate` wraps around the `RATES` array correctly (`0.75 → 1`); progress bar width computed correctly when `s.total === 0` (avoid `NaN%`).
- **`Reader`**: `Navigate` redirect when `book` is undefined or `n` is `NaN` (e.g. `/book/x/read/abc`); keyboard nav (`ArrowRight`/`ArrowLeft`/`Escape`) respecting `hasChapterFile` boundaries; `finishChapter` navigates to next chapter vs back to map depending on availability; autoplay-into-next-chapter flow (`autoplayRef`).
- **`BookMap`**: redirect on missing book; `MapChapterCard` toggles read state; "Mark the map as read" button hidden once `mapRead` is true.
- **`Library`**: search filtering via `searchBooks`, `/` keyboard shortcut focuses search input *except* when another input is focused, `ContinueStrip` hides when `pct >= 100` or no progress exists, empty-library state when `books.length === 0`.

